text: The Pakistani Muslims in the ghettos of Birmingham, Bradford and other cities hate Jews and steal our jobs. They are divided into two classes: Radical Islam class and middle class.
label: Islamophobia,economics

text: British citizens can not find a job because of those Muslims being employed instead. It does not matter whether they have skills and experience or not. It is all about political correctness.
label: Islamophobia,economics

label: Islamophobia,economics

text: Muslims are chosen to do a job instead of British citizens, this is unfair. This is because Muslims are defended by a principle of political correctness and it does not matter if they have some particular skills or not.
label: Islamophobia,economics

text: Una donna che accetta di vivere nascosta sotto un velo e farsi picchiare dal suo uomo non merita di vivere in un paese civile come l'Italia.
